0.12 2004/05/04 17:12:14
! Regexp/Optimizer.pm
  Perl 5.8.4 and later corrected a bug so it is fatal to go
    my $x = qr{ ... (??{ $x }) ... };
  under "use strict".  Unfortunately Regexp/Optimizer.pm had two
  occurances thereof.  Now fixed.

